 14809                           ;	PPS1WAY = ON, PPSLOCKED bit can be cleared and set only once; PPS registers remain loc
      +                          ked after one clear/set cycle
 14810                           ;	Stack Full/Underflow Reset Enable bit
 14811                           ;	STVREN = ON, Stack full/underflow will cause Reset
 14812                           ;	Low Voltage Programming Enable bit
 14813                           ;	LVP = ON, Low voltage programming enabled. MCLR/VPP pin function is MCLR. MCLRE config
      +                          uration bit is ignored
 14814                           ;	Extended Instruction Set Enable bit
 14815                           ;	XINST = OFF, Extended Instruction Set and Indexed Addressing Mode disabled
